Package com.isotrol.impe3.pms.api

Interface Summary
Described Interace for a DTO with name and a description.
WithCorrectness Interface for DTOs with correctness.
WithId Interface for DTOs that contain an ID.
WithLocalizedNameDTO Interace for a DTO with default name and localized name.
WithState Interface for DTOs with state.
 

Class Summary
AbstractDescribed Abstract superclass for described DTOs.
AbstractDescribedWithId Abstract DTO with id, name and description.
AbstractRoutable Abstract class for DTOs that contain state, an ID, and a routable flag.
AbstractTreeIndex<E extends WithId,T extends AbstractTreeDTO<E,T>> DTO for a tree of selection DTOs.
AbstractWithId Abstract class for DTOs that contain an ID.
AbstractWithState Abstract class for DTOs that contain state information.
AbstractWithStateAndId Abstract class for DTOs that contain state and an ID.
AbstractWithStateAndIdAndCorrectness Abstract class for DTOs that contain and id, state and correctness status.
GlobalAuthorityMap Global authorities hierarchy.
Inherited<V> DTO that represents a inherited value in a portal.
NameDTO DTO representing a combination of a display name and path segment.
PortalAuthorityMap Portal authorities hierarchy.
PropertyDTO DTO representing a string-valued property.
ValidModuleDTO Abstract DTO for a valid module description.
 

Enum Summary
Correctness Enumeration of the possible "correctness" states of certain objects.
GlobalAuthority Global authorities enumeration.
GlobalRole Global roles enumeration.
PortalAuthority Portal authorities enumeration.
State Enumeration of the possible states of objects with a lifecycle.
 

Exception Summary
AuthorizationException Exception thrown when the user is not authorized to perform an operation.
EntityException Base class for PMS Entity Exceptions.
EntityInUseException Exception thrown when a requested entity cannot be deleted because it is being used.
EntityNotFoundException Exception thrown when a requested entity is not found.
InvalidImportFileException Exception thrown when an import file can't be parsed.
InvalidOperationException Exception thrown when the requested operation cannot be performed.
NoSessionException Exception thrown when the user is not authorized to perform an operation because it has no session.
PMSException Base class for PMS Exceptions.
